        <dct:description xml:lang="fr-FR"><![CDATA[,"exercice":"[b]Tracez en rouge les diagonales des 2 carrés 8x8.[/b][br][br][svg]<rect x='0' y='0' width='8' height='8' style='fill:white;'/><rect x='24' y='8' width='8' height='8' style='fill:white;'/><line x1='0' y1='0' x2='8' y2='8' style='fill:node;stroke:red;stroke-width:1px;'/><line x1='8' y1='0' x2='0' y2='8' style='fill:node;stroke:red;stroke-width:1px;'/><line x1='24' y1='8' x2='32' y2='16' style='fill:node;stroke:red;stroke-width:1px;'/><line x1='24' y1='16' x2='32' y2='8' style='fill:node;stroke:red;stroke-width:1px;'/>[/svg]","tips":["Les diagonales du [b]premier[/b] carré relient les points [b](0,0) à (7,7)[/b] et [b](0,7) à (7,0)[/b].","Les diagonales du [b]second[/b] carré relient les points [b](24,8) à (31,15)[/b] et [b](24,15) à (31,8)[/b].","[code]RGB(255,0,0)[br]LINE(0,0,7,7)[br]LINE(0,7,7,0)[br]LINE(24,8,31,15)[br]LINE(24,15,31,8)[/code]"]]]></dct:description>
